      "content": "I'm really sorry you're feeling so down, but it's important to remember that it's okay to ask for help. Sometimes, it can feel like you're trying to fix something that can't be fixed, but there are people who care and want to help. You don't have to go through this alone. There are professionals who can help you work through these feelings and find a way to feel better. You are valued and worth reaching out for support.",
      "source": "target",
